{"tid":2447890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣自2月21日起專機從緬甸撤僑兩百多人","createTime":"2021-03-15T13:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T06:29:02.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c959a4cb970505f927ee7cce84a222245c299bf5","tid":2447890,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:39:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">緬甸第2班救援班機 昨日載118人抵台</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/15/3467805_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F15%2F3467805_1_1.jpg&h=728e2293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緬甸局勢持續動盪，華航第2架救援班機已於昨日返抵台灣。非當事航班。（資料照）<br />\n<br />\n2021/03/15 21:10<br />\n〔記者呂伊萱／台北報導〕緬甸情勢動盪，<span class=\"red\">華航執飛自仰光飛往台北的第2班救援班機，已於昨（14）日傍晚搭載118名乘客抵台，其中包括逾80名國人及持居留證人士。</span><br />\n<br />\n緬甸政府自2020年4月暫停所有國際商業航班飛航緬甸，僅特許專案申請的「救援班機」（relief flight）在緬甸境內起降。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人歐江安今天表示，我駐緬甸代表處每月協助華航申請「台北-仰光」航線的飛航許可，載運救援物資及特許的旅客，運作順暢。<span class=\"red\">第一架救援班機於2月21日乘載超過80位旅客返台。</span><br />\n<br />\n歐江安說，根據我駐緬甸代表處掌握資訊，第2架救援班機已於14日近中午自緬甸仰光起飛，下午5時許平安飛抵台北，該班機載有乘客118名，其中包括超過80名國人及持居留證人士。第2架救援班機是由華航執飛，我駐緬甸代表處協助申請飛航許可。<br />\n<br />\n駐緬甸代表處於1月29日起提醒台商及僑胞密切注意緬甸政治情勢發展，並隨時與駐處保持聯繫。駐處也多次更新政情新聞，<span class=\"red\">並主動聯繫台商，協助可能面臨的困難。駐處在2月5日及3月1日陸續發布新聞周知台商有關華航航班消息，請規劃返國者聯繫華航。</span>駐處並與華航保持聯繫，並對有需要的國人，提供及時協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3467805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3467805&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=9da78a7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3467805&h=c71f92e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3467805</a>"},{"pid":"ee7962b32c2e1b1099929286c84c43b141dbc08a","tid":2447890,"uid":282637,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iCGEa7.jpg&amp;h=f7a024bc&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"bec4c989fdffa21d4ed70cf5d1edbfc245887fa5","tid":2447890,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:47:30.000Z","msg":"中国吳京呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e008dc5bab0ee2f4fb8c7db4ec2e3541e98723","tid":2447890,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee7962b32c2e1b1099929286c84c43b141dbc08a","tid":2447890,"uid":282637,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iCGEa7.jpg&amp;h=f7a024bc&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:47:56.000Z","msg":"戰狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e22b05c56418c26ef2fbf7e9ad165c2bc73ec8a","tid":2447890,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bec4c989fdffa21d4ed70cf5d1edbfc245887fa5","tid":2447890,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:47:30.000Z","msg":"中国吳京呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"忙著幫口交部口交"},{"pid":"79bfb86d2c3f6636c8df5427905a55853827995f","tid":2447890,"uid":244612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c959a4cb970505f927ee7cce84a222245c299bf5","tid":2447890,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:39:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">緬甸第2班救援班機 昨日載118人抵台</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/